OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,FThere should not be an outright
OL,7,Fnationwide ban on smartphones in Welsh
OL,8,Fschools, according to a new report.
OL,10,FInstead the Welsh Government is being
OL,11,Furged to produce clear guidance and a
OL,12,Frobust framework to allow teachers to
OL,13,Fset their own rules in schools.
OL,15,FThe Senedd's Petitions Committee said
OL,16,Fthat although smartphones could cause
OL,17,Fharm there was also evidence of the
OL,18,Fdevices supporting young people's
OL,19,Fwelfare and safety.
