OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,FCommittee members spoke to teachers,
OL,7,Fpupils and parents and considered the
OL,8,Fdifferent rules adopted by schools,
OL,9,Fand the complex relationship between
OL,10,Fyoung people and their smartphones.
OL,12,FIn its report, the committee urged the
OL,13,FWelsh Government to establish clear
OL,14,Fguidance, alongside a robust decision-
OL,15,Fmaking framework for teachers and
OL,16,Fschools.
