OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,FThe report was produced following a
OL,7,Fpetition that was signed by more than
OL,8,F3,000 people and called for a ban in
OL,9,Fschools, except in exceptional
OL,10,Fcircumstances.
OL,12,FCommittee chairwoman Carolyn Thomas
OL,13,Fsaid: "The growing body of evidence
OL,14,Fabout the harms of smartphones
OL,15,Foutweighing the benefits for children
OL,16,Fis both compelling and concerning.
OL,18,F"However, on balance we do not believe
OL,19,Fthat it supports a move to a uniform
OL,20,F'ban' on smartphones in all Welsh
OL,21,Fschools.
