OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,F"Every so often a petition comes in
OL,7,Fthat grabs our attention and sometimes
OL,8,Fthings that seem the simplest, are
OL,9,Fmuch, much more complex once you
OL,10,Fscratch the surface.
OL,12,F"We thank the petitioner for bringing
OL,13,Fforward this very timely issue, which
OL,14,Fgave us the opportunity to explore and
OL,15,Fpresent the recommendations to Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment.
OL,18,F"We hope the information will be
OL,19,Fuseful for all schools in considering
OL,20,Fand setting their policies."
