OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,FThe evidence gathered by the
OL,7,Fcommittee, along with its
OL,8,Frecommendations, will now be
OL,9,Fconsidered by the Welsh Government.
OL,11,FIn response, The Welsh Government says:
OL,13,F"Almost all schools in Wales have
OL,14,Fmobile phone policies, which can
OL,15,Finclude banning them during lessons or
OL,16,Fat breaktime.
OL,18,F"We are working with schools to ensure
OL,19,Fthey have policies and resources to
OL,20,Freduce the negative impacts of mobile
OL,21,Fphones and promote learning.
