OL,3,CNo nationwide smartphone ban in Welsh
OL,4,Cschools, report recommends
OL,6,F"The Education Secretary is due to
OL,7,Fmeet with Ofcom shortly to discuss
OL,8,Fmobile phone and social media usage.
OL,9,FWe will consider the report's
OL,10,Frecommendations."
OL,12,FA debate will be arranged in the
OL,13,FSenedd in due course.
OL,15,FIn England, there is not an outright
OL,16,Fban but UK Government guidance
OL,17,Fencourages schools to prohibit the use
OL,18,Fof phones.
